# Netlify redirects

# Template routing. /contact still resolves to index.html until Phase 9 adds
# the Contact template — the home shell shows a placeholder for it. Any
# other unmatched path is treated as a project slug and serves project.html;
# its main.js inspects the slug and either renders the project (Phase 6) or
# silently redirects to / when the slug is unknown.
/contact   /index.html     200
/*         /project.html   200

# Phase 12 will add 301s for legacy hash URLs listed in BUILD_SPEC.md §4
# (/#morro -> /morro, /#gestion_reaviva -> /reaviva, etc.).
